deoxicit/Prism.summary: Recent activities in the deoxicit/Prism repository have focused on code enhancements and feature additions, including ESLint fixes, the introduction of new contracts, and improvements to upgradable contracts. Additionally, maintenance pages have been added, and certain features such as Linea support have been removed. The repository has also seen updates to article sorting, the introduction of a project logo, and metadata adjustments. Furthermore, pagination issues have been addressed, showcasing ongoing development and refinement.

BasedHardware/omi.summary: The BasedHardware/omi repository has witnessed significant activity with the submission of a pull request titled 'Kidwise-App-Integration'. This integration aims to revolutionize childhood development by transforming the Omi into an AI-powered tracker, providing real-time insights and creating a development diary for children's growth journeys, highlighting innovative applications of the technology.
